Class AQueryBuilderDecorator

java.lang.Object
org.opencastproject.assetmanager.impl.AQueryBuilderDecorator
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.opencastproject.assetmanager.api.query.AQueryBuilder
public class AQueryBuilderDecorator extends Object implements org.opencastproject.assetmanager.api.query.AQueryBuilder
A wrapper for query builder. All method calls are delegated to the wrapped builder by default. Override to provide extra functionality.
